        <h1>Bexhill Prostate Cancer Support</h1>
        <h2>Providing support and advice for those affected with prostate cancer in Bexhill and surrounding areas.</h2>
        <p>
            Bexhill Prostate Cancer Support was setup in 2016 to provide support and advice for those living with
            prostate cancer in Bexhill and surrounding areas.  Meetings are on the first Monday of the month, starting March 7th 2016,
            from 7-9pm at Bexhill Hospital, in the Health Centre building.  There will be a break with no mettings in July and August.
            Meetings provide a chance for people to chat and share experiences as well as to hear from experts.
        </p>
    </section>
